{
  "scene": {
    "id": "chapter1_scene01",
    "title": "序章 - 人群中的觉醒",
    "background": "/images/black.png"
  },
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "asset": "/images/black.png",
      "transition": "fade"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "……",
      "backgroundChange": "/images/black.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/q1.png",
      "effects": {
        "shake": true,
        "duration": 0.5,
        "transition": "fade"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "qxn",
      "text": "……我做了什么……"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "秦小南瘫坐在地，身后风声呼啸，仿佛天地都在指责他的罪孽"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/jiuku.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "qxn",
      "text": "……完了……我杀人了……我……该死……"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/y1.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "昏暗的藏身处，火光摇曳，哑巴少女缓缓走来"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『你没有杀人。那是陶瓷人偶。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "qxn",
      "text": "（猛地抬头，瞳孔收缩）……你说什么？"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/ch.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『是他做的实验——“活人桩”。里面封的是残魂。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『他认为这样可以规避死亡预告。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "秦小南眼神动摇，身躯颤抖"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "effects": {
        "fadeout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/q2.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "qxn",
      "text": "这……这一切……都是试探？都是骗局？！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『他在考验你，折磨你。你只是个工具人。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "一瞬的沉寂后，秦小南怒吼着站起，眼神里满是怒火"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/lcbs.png",
      "effects": {
        "shake": true,
        "duration": 0.5
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "qxn",
      "text": "我要杀了他！我要把他和他的那些跟班都杀掉！"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/y1.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『你要听我的故事吗？关于我，和他。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "少女眼神比火焰还要炽热，她缓缓写下..."
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/black.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadeout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『我曾经是异端，他救了我……也毁了所有人。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/cz.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/yb2.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "少女小时候被选中成为弥陀的代言人，代价是天生不能说话。"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "少女只能在本子上写字与弥陀交流。"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "弥陀想要了解人间，少女想要了解弥陀。"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/yd2.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "村里的人发现后，大骂女孩是异端。"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/black.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadeout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/ss2.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "他们拿着火把要把女孩烧死。"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/ss2.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadeout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/lcb.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『他问弥陀：我的寿命能超过5分钟吗？』"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/lcb.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadeout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/fou.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『弥陀说，否。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "effects": {
        "fadeout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『于是，他选择献祭全村，换我一命。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/black.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "……"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/1s.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/2s.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/3s.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『那尊佛像，从天而降。村子，被抹去了。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "qxn",
      "text": "这就是那场连环杀人案？你们……"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/ds.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『他向弥陀许愿，但愿望里没有“信仰”，只有“恨”。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『所以他才有瑕疵。才变成了要被弥陀“抹除”的存在。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "effects": {
        "fadeout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "乌山之巅，夜色下的大佛低头，头颅处隐现一道细裂"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgchange",
      "background": "/images/lh.png",
      "effects": {
        "fadein": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『裂缝开始了。弥陀要寻求自保。时间不多了。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "tanchuang",
      "tc": "/images/y5.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "ybsn",
      "text": "『你，要阻止他。』"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "本章结束，谢谢游玩"
    }
  ]
}